<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <h1>About Modelarium</h1>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <a href="/Chat" class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-comment-alt me-2"></i>Chat
                    </a>
                    <a href="/Models" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
                        <i class="fas fa-microchip me-2"></i>Models
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mb-4">
            <div class="card bg-dark h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="text-danger mb-4">Welcome to Modelarium</h2>

                    <p class="lead">
                        Your personal AI assistant powered by state-of-the-art language models
                    </p>

                    <hr class="my-4 border-secondary">

                    <h4 class="mb-3">Our Mission</h4>
                    <p>
                        At Modelarium, we're dedicated to making advanced artificial intelligence accessible to everyone.
                        Our platform provides a seamless interface to interact with cutting-edge language models,
                        allowing you to get instant help, generate content, solve problems, and explore new ideas.
                    </p>

                    <h4 class="mb-3 mt-4">What Makes Us Different</h4>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-secondary">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5><i class="fas fa-bolt text-warning me-2"></i>Performance</h5>
                                    <p class="mb-0">
                                        Our platform is optimized for speed and efficiency, providing near-instant responses even with complex queries.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-secondary">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5><i class="fas fa-lock text-primary me-2"></i>Privacy-Focused</h5>
                                    <p class="mb-0">
                                        Your conversations stay private and secure. We don't store or use your data to train our models.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-secondary">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5><i class="fas fa-cogs text-info me-2"></i>Customizable</h5>
                                    <p class="mb-0">
                                        Fine-tune your experience with adjustable parameters and model selection for different use cases.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-secondary">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5><i class="fas fa-robot text-danger me-2"></i>Multiple Models</h5>
                                    <p class="mb-0">
                                        Choose from various AI models like Llama2, Mistral, and Phi-3 to suit your specific needs.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h4 class="mb-3 mt-4">Our Technology</h4>
                    <p>
                        We leverage the latest advancements in large language models (LLMs) to power our chat interface.
                        These models have been trained on diverse datasets to understand and generate human-like text across
                        a wide range of topics and domains.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our platform currently supports:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Ollama (CLI)</strong></li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4 class="mb-3 mt-4">Use Cases</h4>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-dark border-secondary h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="text-primary mb-3"><i class="fas fa-code me-2"></i>Coding Assistant</h5>
                                    <p>
                                        Get help with programming, debug code, or learn new programming concepts with practical examples.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-dark border-secondary h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="text-success mb-3"><i class="fas fa-pen me-2"></i>Content Creation</h5>
                                    <p>
                                        Generate creative writing, brainstorm ideas, or get help drafting emails and documents.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                            <div class="card bg-dark border-secondary h-100">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h5 class="text-warning mb-3"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-2"></i>Learning</h5>
                                    <p>
                                        Explore complex topics, get explanations, or prepare for exams with personalized tutoring.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

